results.description:
Generally considered to be the first title of the Golden Age dedicated to the horror genre, Adventures into the Unknown was published from 1948 to 1967.

Collected Editions

  • Adventures Into the Unknown Archives vol. 1 (#1-4)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 1 (#1-5)
  • Adventures Into the Unknown Archives vol. 2 (#5-8)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 2 (#6-10)
  • Adventures Into the Unknown Archives vol. 3 (#9-12)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 3 (#11-15)
  • Adventures Into the Unknown Archives vol. 4 (#13-16)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 4 (#16-20)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 5 (#21-25)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 6 (#26-30)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 7 (#31-36)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 8 (#37-43)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 9 (#44-50)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 10 (#51-57)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 11 (#58-64)
  • ACG Collected Works: Adventures Into the Unknown vol. 12 (#65-71)
  • The Complete Spirit of Frankenstein (S/F series from #5-10, 12)
